<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>fuzhy blog</title><link>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/</link><description>Recent content on fuzhy blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 May 2021 22:15:28 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>About</title><link>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/about/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 May 2021 21:38:52 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/about/</guid><description>&lt;p>This is fuzhy, a programmer in Beijing.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Blog Setup</title><link>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/post/2021-05-12-blog-setup/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 May 2021 22:15:28 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/post/2021-05-12-blog-setup/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>简要记录本博客的搭建流程和步骤。&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="前提">前提&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>hugo&lt;/li>
&lt;li>git&lt;/li>
&lt;li>github&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="具体步骤">具体步骤&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>github创建公开的repo: &lt;strong>blog&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>hugo设置&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">hugo new site blog
&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> blog
git init
&lt;span class="c1"># theme&lt;/span>
git submodule add https://github.com/xianmin/hugo-theme-jane.git themes/jane
cp -r themes/jane/exampleSite/content ./
cp themes/jane/exampleSite/config.toml ./
&lt;span class="c1"># test: http://localhost:1313/&lt;/span>
hugo server
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="3">
&lt;li>git设置&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">git add .
git commit -m &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;first commit&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/fuzhy/blog.git
git push -u origin main
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="4">
&lt;li>github actions的workflow设置&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">mkdir -p .github/workflows
touch .github/workflows/gh-pages.yaml
&lt;span class="c1"># gh-pages.yaml reference: https://github.com/peaceiris/actions-gh-pages&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="c1"># commit &amp;amp; push&lt;/span>
git add .
git commit -m &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;add gh-pages workflow&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
git push
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="5">
&lt;li>pages设置。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>首先可以看到actions工作流执行成功的记录，并且自动创建了git的gh-pages分支&lt;/li>
&lt;li>打开Settings设置，选择Pages，Source中选择上面创建的gh-pages分支，Save保存。（folder选择默认的/root）&lt;/li>
&lt;li>过一段时间后访问https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/即可生效。但是此时好像没有css等文件（网页检查可发现）&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;ol start="6">
&lt;li>修改配置&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>没有样式的原因是config的baseURL配置错误，需要改成https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/&lt;/li>
&lt;li>同时改一下其他的配置并提交。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;ol start="7">
&lt;li>debug&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>改完之后github action直接deploy出错，根据错误日志，查询大概需要extended版本的hugo：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">Error: Error building site: TOCSS: failed to transform &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;sass/jane.scss&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>text/x-scss&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span>. Check your Hugo installation&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> you need the extended version to build SCSS/SASS
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>于是修改action的配置，新增extended模式。==&amp;gt;action部署不再报错，搞定。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/marketplace/actions/hugo-setup#%EF%B8%8F-use-hugo-extended">https://github.com/marketplace/actions/hugo-setup#%EF%B8%8F-use-hugo-extended&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;ol start="8">
&lt;li>初版搞定&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>功能：提交源文件到main分支，action自动build/deloy到gh-pages分支，网站自动更新&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="迁移">迁移&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>后期需要迁移，或者在其他电脑更新blog时，只需：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">git clone --recursive https://github.com/fuzhy/blog.git
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Hello World</title><link>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/post/2021-05-11-hello-world/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 May 2021 22:37:56 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://fuzhy.github.io/blog/post/2021-05-11-hello-world/</guid><description>&lt;p>This is the first blog for &lt;code>hello world&lt;/code>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>